sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Nguoi dung
    participant FE as Frontend Chat UI
    participant API as Backend API
    participant SVC as ChatbotService
    participant DB as MongoDB / Redis
    participant FL as Flask Rasa API
    participant RASA as Rasa Server
    participant ACT as Action Server

    U->>FE: Nhap cau hoi
    FE->>FE: Tao conversationId neu chua co
    FE->>FE: Hien thi user message tam thoi
    FE->>API: POST /api/v1/chatbot/{id}/chat
    API->>API: Rate limit + validate params/body
    API->>SVC: chat(chatbotId, body)
    SVC->>DB: Lay chatbot runtime tu cache/setting/default
    DB-->>SVC: ip, flaskPort, botId
    SVC->>FL: POST /chat voi message, sender_id, conversation_id
    FL->>RASA: POST /webhooks/rest/webhook
    RASA->>RASA: NLU parse intent, confidence, entities
    RASA->>RASA: Core chon next action theo tracker/policy
    alt Action la utter_*
        RASA-->>FL: Domain response text/buttons
    else Action tuy bien
        RASA->>ACT: Goi custom action
        ACT-->>RASA: Events va response
        RASA-->>FL: Bot response
    end
    opt Nguoi dung da dang nhap
        FL->>DB: Luu conversation vao MongoDB
    end
    FL-->>SVC: ApiResponse {responses}
    SVC->>DB: Gan messageId/sourceType va luu ChatMessage
    SVC-->>API: successResponse(enrichedResponses)
    API-->>FE: 200 OK
    FE->>FE: Them bot messages voi recipient_id = bot
    FE-->>U: Hien thi phan hoi chatbot
